						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Remote-sensing-and-GIS/Related-developments/AGRHYMET-Regional-Centre" title="AGRHYMET Regional Centre " alt="link">AGRHYMET Regional Centre </a></h2>

	
					<p>Recent AGRHYMET products include: Seasonal forecasts of rainfall, flow rates and agro-climatological advice for the rainy season of 2013 in West Africa, Cameroon and Chad; Satellite based rainfall estimates; and Notice on the agricultural and food prospects in the Sahel and in West Africa. &nbsp;(<a href="http://www.agrhymet.ne/eng/?utm_source=K4DNewsletterEN&amp;utm_medium=Link&amp;utm_campaign=K4D_EN_May2013" target="_self">AGRHYMET</a>, 2013)</p>
